result.execSummary:
The defendant was charged with both OWI (7th, 8th or 9th w/ Passenger < 16 Yrs Old) and Operating w/ PAC-Passenger < 16 Yrs (7th, 8th or 9th) [Modifiers: With a Minor Child in the Vehicle]. The defendant was found guilty of OWI (7th, 8th or 9th w/ Passenger < 16 Yrs Old) and the other charge, Operating w/ PAC-Passenger < 16 Yrs (7th, 8th or 9th) [Modifiers: With a Minor Child in the Vehicle] was dismissed by the court.

  • Theresa M Heck was found guilty of OWI (7th, 8th or 9th w/ Passenger < 16 Yrs Old), an unclassified felony, Wisconsin Statutes 346.63(1)(a).
